//   - Editor: ActionSnapshot, ActionDiff, ChangeLog, AgentTask,
//     ReviewQueueEntry, VersionBranch, EditCheckpoint, DatasetSnapshot,
//     SnapshotChangeRecord
//   - Copilot: CopilotConversation, CopilotMessage
//   - Studio/test: StudioReport, CardReport, SimulationSnapshot, test_*
// =====================================================================
